# Base URL of the NestJS backend API.
# - For iOS Simulator: http://localhost:3000
# - For Android Emulator: http://10.0.2.2:3000
# - For Physical Device (Expo Go): http://<YOUR_COMPUTER_LOCAL_IP>:3000 (e.g., http://192.168.1.50:3000)
#
# IMPORTANT: When testing on a physical phone, do NOT use 'localhost' or '127.0.0.1'.
# You must specify your computer's local network IP address.
